title: Below Deck Med: Broken Arrow
description:
The self help douche ends his trip on Below Deck Med. Will he come through and stab Zim in the throat?
This week's bonus episode is about HBO shows, Big Brother, and Housewives books on Amazon.. To hear it, become a Patreon member at Patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens.
